menu "PZEM"

config DEV_MOCK_PZEM
    bool "Use mock PZEM readings (development only)"
    default n
    help
        When enabled, pzem_measure_cycle generates synthetic power samples
        instead of reading the PZEM-004T over UART. Use only on development
        benches without the sensor wired. Never enable in production firmware.

endmenu
